# NETWORK::NETWORK_IS_GAMER_IN_MY_SESSION

## Parameters
* **GAMER_HANDLE\*** gamerHandle

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Returns TRUE if the player represented by this gamer handle is in the same session
